The paper presents a distributed full-text index for big data applications, which involves data structures and algorithms for efficient indexing and querying of large amounts of text data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer science sub-categories of data structures (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), distributed computing (cs.DC), distributed systems (cs.Distributed), and databases (cs.DB).
